马尔伯洛市有一所公立高中[https://web.archive.org/web/20141021073427/http://www.frhsd.com/marlboro/ 馬爾伯洛高中]（Marlboro High School），创于1968年，隶属于菲力荷高中学区（Freehold Regional High School District）提供九至十二年级的高中教育。该高中学区涵盖了{{le|科爾茨內克鎮區 (新澤西州)|Colts Neck Township, New Jersey|科爾茨內克鎮區}}、{{le|英吉利敦 (新澤西州)|Englishtown, New Jersey|英吉利敦}}、{{le|法明代爾 (新澤西州)|Farmingdale, New Jersey|法明代爾}}、[[菲力荷自治市|菲力荷自治市]]、{{le|弗里霍爾德鎮區 (新澤西州)|Freehold Township, New Jersey|弗里霍爾德鎮區}}、{{le|豪厄爾鎮區 (新澤西州)|Howell Township, New Jersey|豪厄爾鎮區}}和{{le|馬納拉潘鎮區 (新澤西州)|Manalapan Township, New Jersey|馬納拉潘鎮區}}<ref>[http://education.state.nj.us/rc/rc07/narrative/25/1650/25-1650-000.html Freehold Regional High School District 2007 Report Card Narrative] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080927181203/http://education.state.nj.us/rc/rc07/narrative/25/1650/25-1650-000.html |date=2008-09-27 }}, [[New_Jersey_Department_of_Education|New Jersey Department of Education]]. Accessed 4月28日, 2008. "Freehold Regional High School District, the largest high school district in New Jersey, has six high schools with almost 12,000 students and over 1,500 employees.... District members include the Townships of Colts Neck, Freehold, Howell, Manalapan, and Marlboro, and the Boroughs of Englishtown, Farmingdale, and Freehold."</ref> 等市镇。有些马尔伯洛市的学生到同样隶属于这个高中学区的[[Colts_Neck|Colts Neck]]高中上学。有许多马尔伯洛市的学生到学区内各种学科的加强班上学。同样的，其他市镇的学生也到马尔伯洛高中的商业加强班上学。

